text:
Sunniva Høiåsen Frigstad (born 2000 in Vennesla, Norway) is a Norwegian beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned Miss Universe Norway 2020.
Personal life.
Frigstad was born and raised in Vennesla. She currently studying marketing and management University of Agder.
Miss Norway 2020.
Frigstad began her pageantry career representing Agder in the Miss Norway 2020 competition on October 31, 2020, where she was crowned as Miss Universe Norway 2020.
Miss Universe 2020.
Frigstad will represent Norway at the Miss Universe 2020 pageant.
